microservice.infrastructure.controllers.admin

Class CRUDAbstractController<E extends ModelInterface,S extends CRUDServiceInterface<E>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • microservice.infrastructure.controllers.admin.CRUDAbstractController<E,S>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CRUDGroupController, CRUDUserController

    public abstract class CRUDAbstractController<E extends ModelInterface,S extends CRUDServiceInterface<E>>
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract implementation of a CRUD controller. This abstract implementation expect a POJO object to be created. The POJO object must implement ModelInterface
